# EdUsaathiAI Web App — Implementation Plan

## Overview

A student-facing web portal built inside `website/` — the same Supabase backend, same edge
functions, same 20 Saathi verticals. Students who cannot install the Expo mobile app can 
use this on any browser. Also serves as the investor demo URL.

