## Tech Stack

| Layer | Choice | Why |
|---|---|---|
| Framework | Next.js 15 App Router | SSR, streaming, server actions |
| Language | TypeScript strict | Consistent with mobile + admin |
| Styling | Tailwind CSS v4 | CSS-first config, faster |
| Components | shadcn/ui | Accessible, themeable, battle-tested |
| Animation | Framer Motion v11 | Investor-ready transitions |
| Backend | Supabase JS v2 | Same DB, Auth, Edge Functions |
| State | Zustand | Lightweight, no boilerplate |
| Data fetching | React Query v5 (TanStack) | Caching, real-time, mutations |
| Error tracking | Sentry | Already have DSN |
| Deploy | Vercel | Same org, zero config |

