## Proposed Changes

### 1 — Scaffold

#### [NEW] `website/` — Next.js 15 app

- `npx create-next-app@latest website --typescript --tailwind --app --src-dir no --import-alias "@/*"`
- Install: `shadcn@latest`, `framer-motion`, `@supabase/ssr`, `@supabase/supabase-js`, `zustand`, `@tanstack/react-query`, `@sentry/nextjs`
- Tailwind v4: replace `tailwind.config.js` with CSS `@import "tailwindcss"` approach

---

### 2 — Auth Layer

#### [NEW] `website/middleware.ts`
- Reads Supabase session from cookie
- Redirects `/` and `/(dashboard)/**` to `/login` if unauthenticated
- Redirects `/login` and `/signup` to `/saathis` if already logged in

#### [NEW] `website/lib/supabase/client.ts` + `server.ts`
- Uses `@supabase/ssr` package (Next.js 15 compatible cookie handling)
- Server client uses `cookies()` from `next/headers`

#### [NEW] `website/app/(auth)/login/page.tsx`
- Email + OTP (same as mobile)
- Animated with Framer Motion fadeUp

#### [NEW] `website/app/(auth)/signup/page.tsx`
- Email, full_name, password

#### [NEW] `website/app/(auth)/profile-setup/page.tsx`
- Multi-step wizard: name → exam target → preferred tone → primary saathi

---

### 3 — Dashboard Shell

#### [NEW] `website/app/(dashboard)/layout.tsx`
- Left sidebar (desktop): logo, saathi nav links, profile, logout
- Bottom tab bar (mobile)
- Reads auth, redirects if unauthenticated

---

### 4 — Saathi Selection

#### [NEW] `website/app/(dashboard)/saathis/page.tsx`
- Same 20-card grid as landing page but interactive
- Click → routes to `/chat/[id]`
- Preserves last-used saathi via Zustand

#### [NEW] `website/lib/constants/saathis.ts`
- All 20 saathis with `id`, `name`, `emoji`, `tagline`, `primary`, `accent` colours

---

### 5 — Chat Interface

#### [NEW] `website/app/(dashboard)/chat/[id]/page.tsx`
- Calls `POST /functions/v1/chat` with `Authorization: Bearer <session_token>`
- **Streaming** via `ReadableStream` — text appears word by word
- Message history stored in React Query cache (per saathi)
- Input: textarea with Shift+Enter support

#### [NEW] `website/hooks/useChat.ts`
- Handles streaming response from the edge function
- Mutation with optimistic UI

---

### 6 — News Feed

#### [NEW] `website/app/(dashboard)/news/page.tsx`
- Filter tabs per vertical
- Reads from `news_items` table via Supabase JS (RLS: authenticated = can read active items)
- Paginated with React Query `useInfiniteQuery`

---

### 7 — Error Tracking

#### [NEW] `website/sentry.client.config.ts` + `sentry.server.config.ts`
- Uses existing `SENTRY_DSN`

